      "content": "i get the drama thing but it feels weird that the first thing that popped into your head for this specific group was \"riot\" or \"tension.\" like, if this was a group of white suburbanites protesting a new zoning law, would you have jumped straight to \"riot\" too, or would you have just gone with something like \"Community Concerns at 5th and Main\"? it feels like there's a certain way you're framing this specific crowd.",
